{"word":"στέφανος","slug":"στέφανος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>στέφανος, ου, ὁ</el></b> [<el>στέφω</el> ‘encircle, wreath’] <b>wreath/crown,</b> in the Mediterranean world a symbol of distinction<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> specific <b><a href='B:470 27:29'>Mt 27:29</a>; <a href='B:480 15:17'>Mk 15:17</a>; <a href='B:500 19:2'>J 19:2</a>, <a href='B:500 19:5'>5</a>; <a href='B:730 12:1'>Rv 12:1</a>.</b> Cp. <b><a href='B:530 9:25'>1 Cor 9:25</a>; <a href='B:730 9:7'>Rv 9:7</a>; <a href='B:730 14:14'>14:14</a>.</b> Metaph. <b><a href='B:570 4:1'>Phil 4:1</a>; <a href='B:590 2:19'>1 Th 2:19</a>; <a href='B:620 4:8'>2 Ti 4:8</a>; <a href='B:660 1:12'>Js 1:12</a>; <a href='B:670 5:4'>1 Pt 5:4</a>; <a href='B:730 2:10'>Rv 2:10</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> non-specific<b> <a href='B:730 3:11'>Rv 3:11</a>; <a href='B:730 4:4'>4:4</a>, <a href='B:730 4:10'>10</a>; <a href='B:730 6:2'>6:2</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:Στεφανᾶς\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:Στέφανος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}